  "informal_statement": "Choosing k items from n is the same as choosing which n-k items to leave out: the binomial coefficient is symmetric, choose n k = choose n (n-k), for k <= n.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Directly `Nat.choose_symm` (stated as `choose n (n-k) = choose n k`), flipped with `.symm`.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem choose_symm' (n k : ℕ) (hk : k ≤ n) : Nat.choose n k = Nat.choose n (n - k)",
